## The Real Product Isn’t Equipment, It’s Peace of Mind.

My first realization was that this company wasn’t really in the business of renting out speakers and screens.

We were selling a hassle free experience.

This was immediately clear from their service oriented packages.

The **[MICE Pack](/packages/mice/)** for corporate events, for instance, includes a dedicated technician for up to 6 hours.

The **[Wedding Pack](/packages/wedding/)** goes even further, bundling transport, setup, on site support, and post event pickup into the [price](https://malagaeventgear.com/#pricing).

This completely shifts the value proposition.

You aren’t just renting hardware and hoping for the best.

You’re buying a guaranteed, smooth running event.

It’s the difference between being handed a box of tools and being given a finished product.

As one customer, perfectly summarized it:

> I am really satisfied with this team. They exceeded my expectations. Having a meeting in Malaga, it was a huge help that I did not have to worry about the visual solutions and the sound. They made it easy and smooth.

